data.description: Welcome home to this beautifully maintained condo in the heart of Kentlands.  Rare ground-level unit seconds away from Kentlands with fresh paint, HW floors, and a bright kitchen. Two spacious bedrooms with a peaceful garden views.  In-unit washer/dryer, balcony, and ample visitor parking.  3 year new Hot Water Heater.   No steps required to access unit.  Central Gaithersburg location near shops, dining, and commuter routes. Prime location -- easy stroll to nearby shops and restaurants.
